{"tid":12828,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"31歲女做愛時拿熨斗燙男友下體","createTime":"2016-11-29T22:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T20:35:07.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cdc17a5bbf8e6e47958003c2a880f3fec1cb455b","tid":12828,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T22:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20151217/640_5a353df388f6ac9e0937d64151154969.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20151217%2F640_5a353df388f6ac9e0937d64151154969.jpg&h=16dac0f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奈及利亞一名31歲女子阿洛琪(Kenya Alozie)來到英國念書，並在當地交了個男朋友。日前她和男友做愛時，竟突然拿出熨斗燙他的陰莖，還拿砸破的玻璃瓶攻擊他。法官認定阿洛琪犯下嚴重傷人罪，本周一被判有期徒刑9年。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，阿洛琪就讀於考文垂大學(Coventry University)，今年5月因為學生簽證到期必須返為奈及利亞。不過在5月15日她和男友做愛時，卻突然拿出熨斗燙了男友的腿和生殖器，又拿出破玻璃瓶攻擊他，導致男友重傷進行手術。同月24日阿洛琪在機場準備返國時，當場被警方逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，阿洛齊的襲擊明顯是早就計畫好，而且已準備好「武器」，判決反映了案件的嚴重性。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"88ecc314c894fd4eccff58f81e433534cf63e576","tid":12828,"uid":1351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T22:03:20.000Z","msg":"施旖婕係神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d271f793c94eab8cda3f50d3fafc8b5e9625590","tid":12828,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T22:03:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>施旖婕係神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一定係淫西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c10af28ead14187b68e852b3abb2c7cc9d84455","tid":12828,"uid":42372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T00:19:29.000Z","msg":"呢個世界真係咩奇怪野都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab995bedd8714d9f236f65632ae571d650e4a715","tid":12828,"uid":38668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T00